content:
Hagrou is a collective of citizens united by a shared dream: to rethink housing in Brussels to make it more inclusive, more humane, and more connected to its environment.
Our goal? To relearn how to live together, promoting sharing in both everyday life and architecture. We envision a living space where common areas have their rightful place: a community room open to residents and the neighborhood, a shared laundry room, guest rooms for friends, a collaborative workshop&hellip;
Our approach aims to go beyond simple neighborliness: no longer just living side by side, but truly together.
